These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: potato, garlic
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, reading
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, superhero
1. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person eating garlic##8
2. the person eating garlic is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | water      |
| Food          | garlic | potato    |
| Hobby         | reading   | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | satire  | superhero      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
3. the dressmaker is not to the right of the designer##8
4. the person driving the airplane is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | cola        | mirinda    |
| Hobby       | dancing         | rock-climbing |
| Job         | dressmaker | designer   |
| Transport   | airplane               | scooter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, action
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, hip-hop
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, spanish
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the spanish is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
3. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel       | action |
| Music-Genre   | classical       | hip-hop    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | spanish |
| Pet           | goat        | guinea-pig   |

 #################################

 
